data.description: Great opportunity for a move-in campus property!  Relax on the large front porch and enjoy this quiet street just a short block away from Lincoln Avenue and the eastern edge of campus.  The living room fireplace, built in china cabinet, open staircase and hardwood floors throughout the home add to the quality vintage charm.  The kitchen offers plenty of counter and cabinet space.  Three comfortably-sized bedrooms upstairs offer generous closet and storage space.  The unfinished basement offers lots of storage and hobby space to meet your needs. New roof and newer HVAC offer peace of mind.  Freshly painted and ready to move right in! Did I mention the location?  If you are looking for a property close to campus, don't let this one pass you by!
